summary.label:
GPS Waypoints Lite is a surveying application for iOS devices that enables smartphones' users to collect and classify Points and to become map creators. This multi-purpose solution, with an easy-to-use interface, is adequate for both professional activities (such as earth sciences surveying) and personal activities (outdoor and tourism).

The GPS Wpts Lite version includes the following features:
- View current position with accuracy and navigation information;
- Create Points with accuracy information and classify them with Tags;
- View on maps the geodata acquired
- Import Points from CSV files with geographic coordinates (Lat, Long) and KML files with waypoints;
- Export Points to CSV and GPX files by saving data locally or sharing with other applications (e.g. Mail, iCloud/Dropbox/Google Drive);
- Create and use survey's Themes with custom Tags for classifying Points; 
– Backup and restore your data
